64
00:07:56,769 --> 00:08:01,889
-Excuse me, I was here.
-I would have noticed.

65
00:08:02,769 --> 00:08:08,082
I was on the phone, the line moved.
I couldn't move with it...

66
00:08:08,329 --> 00:08:11,639
...because the cord
wouldn't stretch that far!

67
00:08:11,889 --> 00:08:15,723
I'd like to believe you,
but your nose is growing.

68
00:08:16,609 --> 00:08:19,077
Come on!
That was pretty good.

69
00:08:22,889 --> 00:08:27,041
-You realize I could die for this?
-I pee really fast.

70
00:08:27,289 --> 00:08:30,201
I have five brothers, three cousins
and one bathroom.

71
00:08:30,449 --> 00:08:34,567
-I pee faster than anybody.
-A gold medalist.

72
00:08:35,769 --> 00:08:37,327
This I have to see!

73
00:08:49,049 --> 00:08:51,165
I was just about to say that.

74
00:08:52,449 --> 00:08:56,408
I said not to be a pig
in front of our new priest.

75
00:08:58,009 --> 00:09:02,560
-That's Father Alex, to you.
-I'm lsabel.

76
00:09:06,009 --> 00:09:09,319
