Shoot!
I thought I might catch him.

111
00:13:05,049 --> 00:13:09,406
We've been trading calls for months,
but he's always so busy.

112
00:13:09,649 --> 00:13:14,404
-Leave him a note. There's a pad.
-No, no that's okay.

113
00:13:16,689 --> 00:13:20,762
