134
00:15:00,049 --> 00:15:02,005
Quid pro quo, pal.

135
00:15:02,249 --> 00:15:07,721
-Give it to her, she gives it to us.
-I can't do this!

136
00:15:14,289 --> 00:15:15,278
Hello.

137
00:15:16,929 --> 00:15:18,726
I thought....

138
00:15:19,489 --> 00:15:22,686
-I must have the wrong house.
-No! Wait!

139
00:15:23,529 --> 00:15:27,317
-If you want Alex, he's inside.
-He is?

140
00:15:30,689 --> 00:15:32,441
Excuse me. Alex?

141
00:15:33,009 --> 00:15:35,125
-You have a visitor.
-I do?

142
00:15:37,809 --> 00:15:41,688
-Excuse me.
-Well, don't be long.

143
00:15:54,129 --> 00:15:55,118
Isabel!

144
00:15:56,129 --> 00:15:57,562
You remembered.

145
00:15:57,809 --> 00:16:01,165
How could I forget?
I've looked all over for you.

146
00:16:01,409 --> 00:16:04,799
I would have called,
but you disappeared on me.

147
00:16:05,449 --> 00:16:10,239
I didn't know what to do.
I never did anything like that before.

148
00:16:10,569 --> 00:16:14,164
-Going home with a stranger.
-You and me both!

149
00:16:14,409 --> 00:16:17,526
It was just one of those great...

150
00:16:18,409 --> 00:16:19,888
...phenomenal...

151
00:16:20,569 --> 00:16:23,527
...spontaneous things.

152
00:16:25,009 --> 00:16:26,601
Yes, it was.

153
00:16:30,849 --> 00:16:34,637
-So, how long has it been?
-Three months.

154
00:16:35,009 --> 00:16:38,922
Do you mind if I have some?
My stomach is not so good.

155
00:16:39,169 --> 00:16:43,560
Go ahead, help yourself.
Want something to drink? I've got...

156
00:16:44,129 --> 00:16:45,278
...water.

157
00:16:45,529 --> 00:16:47,201
Yeah, water's fine.

158
00:16:51,969 --> 00:16:53,641
You've done a lot here.

159
00:16:54,849 --> 00:16:57,124
Yeah, I've been kind of busy.

160
00:17:04,769 --> 00:17:06,248
You look great.

161
00:17:08,289 --> 00:17:09,404
Thank you.

162
00:17:10,209 --> 00:17:12,279
So, how you been?

163
00:17:14,129 --> 00:17:18,088
-Pregnant.
-Really? Pregnant?

164
00:17:18,649 --> 00:17:22,722
