Congratulations.

165
00:17:23,609 --> 00:17:25,725
Thank you. It's yours.

166
00:17:36,209 --> 00:17:40,521
Mine?
We were together one night.

167
00:17:40,769 --> 00:17:43,841
-That's all it took.
-And I used a condom.

168
00:17:44,529 --> 00:17:47,043
-Lots of them.
-One didn't work.

169
00:17:48,049 --> 00:17:53,806
But, its job is to work!
lts reason for being is to work!

170
00:17:55,529 --> 00:17:56,723
Look...

171
00:17:59,169 --> 00:18:01,444
